dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Trempealeau_Roads_2016.gdb.[Road centerlines for Trempealeau County, Wisconsin. Attributes are based on NENA standards and are MSAG valid where applicable.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://www.tremplocounty.com/tchome/landrecords/data.aspx[Whenever data is updated the metadata is manually updated. This is a QA/QC procedure in order to determine the last update of the dataset.]
